HEADWORD: Implied
<hw>Im*plied"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Virtually involved
or included; involved in substance; inferential; tacitly conceded; --
the correlative of express, or expressed. See <er>Imply</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Impliedly</ent>⟦br⟧
